OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FA legal claim backed by more than
OL,7,F4,500 campaigners about pollution in
OL,8,Fthe rivers Wye, Lugg and Usk, has
OL,9,Fbegun being heard in court today.
OL,11,FCampaigners gathered outside the High
OL,12,FCourt in London where the case,
OL,13,Fdescribed as the largest of its kind,
OL,14,Fis having its first hearing.
OL,16,FThe claim is against chicken producer
OL,17,FAvara Foods Limited and its subsidiary
OL,18,FFreemans of Newent Limited, as well
OL,19,Fthe water company Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,20,FWater.
OL,26,@{D@Ts{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
