OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FThe case argues that Avara's and
OL,7,FFreemans of Newent's farming
OL,8,Foperations, alongside Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,9,FWater's management of the sewer
OL,10,Fsystem, have resulted in widespread
OL,11,Fpollution in the three rivers. All
OL,12,Fthree deny the allegations.
OL,14,FMonday's hearing sees the parties
OL,15,Fappear in court for the first time to
OL,16,Fargue how the claims should be managed
OL,17,Fgoing forward.
OL,26,@pD@Xs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FThe legal claim alleges that pollution
OL,7,Fhas been caused by water run-off from
OL,8,Ffarmland containing high levels of
OL,9,Fphosphorus, nitrogen and bacteria from
OL,10,Fpoultry manure spread on the land as
OL,11,Ffertiliser.
OL,13,FIt also alleges bacteria and nutrient
OL,14,Fpollution in the rivers has been
OL,15,Fcaused by the discharge of sewage
OL,16,Fdirectly into the rivers from Dwr
OL,17,FCymru Welsh Water sewerage systems.
OL,26,@xD@`s{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FLeigh Day, who are the the solicitors
OL,7,Fleading the claim, partner Oliver
OL,8,FHolland said Monday's hearing was an
OL,9,Fimportant first step.
OL,11,FThey said: "There has been a great
OL,12,Fdeal of effort put in by the community
OL,13,Fand environmental campaigners to help
OL,14,Fdrive the proceedings to this point,
OL,15,Fshowing the strength of feeling from
OL,16,Fthose involved about the state of the
OL,17,Frivers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"They feel that the government and
OL,7,Fregulators have not done enough to
OL,8,Fprevent the deterioration of these
OL,9,Frivers, leaving court action as their
OL,10,Fonly option to pursue environmental
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,F"In this hearing, important aspects of
OL,14,Fcase management such as deadlines for
OL,15,Fthe next stages and disclosure of
OL,16,Finformation by both sides will be
OL,17,Fdetermined. We are hoping for a
OL,18,Fpositive outcome, and to be able to
OL,19,Flook ahead to presenting our clients'
OL,20,Farguments in full to the High Court in
OL,21,Fdue course."
OL,26,@uD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FRiver Action's head of legal Emma
OL,7,FDearnaley said the case came at a
OL,8,F"critical time".
OL,10,FShe added: "We believe industrial-
OL,11,Fscale chicken production supplying
OL,12,Fmajor supermarkets and fast-food
OL,13,Fchains has placed immense pressure on
OL,14,Fthe Wye, Lugg and Usk, driving
OL,15,Fnutrient pollution levels that these
OL,16,Fsensitive ecosystems cannot absorb.
OL,17,FSewage pollution must also be reduced
OL,18,Fand stopped to reverse the decline of
OL,19,Fthese rivers.
OL,26,@rD@LOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"River Action supports this claim
OL,7,Fbecause it gives a voice to thousands
OL,8,Fof people who refuse to accept the
OL,9,Fcontinued degradation of their rivers.
OL,10,FCommunities should not have to live
OL,11,Fwith the consequences of sewage
OL,12,Fpollution or an intensive farming
OL,13,Fmodel that we believe pollutes their
OL,14,Fwaterways. This action offers an
OL,15,Fimportant way to hold those allegedly
OL,16,Fresponsible to account and secure the
OL,17,Fsystemic change needed to protect and
OL,18,Frestore our rivers for generations to
OL,19,Fcome."
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
