PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FCampaigners outside the High Court
OL,7,Fspoke about the Significance of the
OL,8,Faction. Justine Evans said the "claim
OL,9,Fis symbolic of what's happening
OL,10,Feverywhere".
OL,12,F"The river is suffering from huge
OL,13,Fquantities, to put it crudely, of poo
OL,14,Fgoing into the river Wye, Usk, and
OL,15,FLugg, Ms Evans added.
OL,17,F"It's essentially run-off from chicken
OL,18,Fmanure and human sewage."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
