FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FAnother campaigner, Lorien Cadier,
OL,7,Fsaid the claim is providing a voice
OL,8,Ffor rivers
OL,10,FShe said: "Our rivers deserve a voice.
OL,11,FThey've been polluted by farmers,
OL,12,Fthey've been polluted by agriculture,
OL,13,Fand road runoff.
OL,15,F"It's almost too late when we realise
OL,16,Fthey are dead and we got to try and
OL,17,Frestore them."
OL,26,@rD@KOUyD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/23
