OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FAvara Foods described the allegations
OL,7,Fas "misconceived" and said it believes
OL,8,Fthe claim is "unsupported by any
OL,9,Fproper science".
OL,11,FIn a statement, the company said:
OL,12,F"This Case Management Conference is a
OL,13,Fprocedural hearing and does not
OL,14,Fconsider the merits of the case.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/23
