OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"The allegations are misconceived and
OL,7,Freflect a misunderstanding of both our
OL,8,Fbusiness and the wider factors
OL,9,Faffecting river health. We are
OL,10,Fconfident in our position and believe
OL,11,Fthe claim is unsupported by any proper
OL,12,Fscientific basis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
