PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"Environment Agency data has noted
OL,7,Fthat there has been a downward trend
OL,8,Fin phosphorus levels which are now
OL,9,Funderstood to be lower than they have
OL,10,Fbeen since the early 1990s. More
OL,11,Fbroadly, independent research makes
OL,12,Fclear that river health is influenced
OL,13,Fby multiple factors that are unrelated
OL,14,Fto our operations.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
