PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"We employ thousands of people and
OL,7,Fpartner with hundreds of farmers to
OL,8,Fhelp feed millions across the UK each
OL,9,Fweek. Around nine in ten people in the
OL,10,FUK eat chicken, and British poultry
OL,11,Fplays a critical role in meeting that
OL,12,Fdemand with affordable, high-quality
OL,13,Ffood produced here in the UK."
OL,15,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water also said it
OL,16,Fbelieved the case was "misguided".
OL,18,FA spokesperson said: "Protecting and
OL,19,Fimproving the environment, including
OL,20,Friver water quality, remains a top
OL,21,Fpriority for the company.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@Bs{zD@VOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/23
