SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"Our work to improve river water
OL,7,Fquality is guided by data and
OL,8,Fassessments from our environmental
OL,9,Fregulators National Resources Wales
OL,10,Fand the Environment Agency.
OL,12,F"Between 2020-2025 we invested more
OL,13,Fthan #76m on reducing nutrient levels
OL,14,Fto improve water quality on the Wye,
OL,15,FLugg and Usk rivers. Ofwat have
OL,16,Fallocated us a further #87m to invest
OL,17,Fbetween 2025-2030 to continue this
OL,18,Fimportant work.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/23
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"We believe this case is misguided and
OL,7,Frisks diverting time and resources
OL,8,Faway from the shared goal of improving
OL,9,Friver water quality.
OL,11,F"Any financial penalties would
OL,12,Fdirectly reduce the funding available
OL,13,Fto invest in essential services and
OL,14,Fdeliver the environmental improvements
OL,15,Four customers expect.
OL,17,F"Dwr Cymru Welsh Water doesn't have
OL,18,Fshareholders and pays no dividends.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOUyD@Cs{
