OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,F"The revenue we receive from customer
OL,7,Fbills is our sole source of funding
OL,8,Ffor maintaining services and upgrading
OL,9,Four infrastructure.
OL,11,F"Without profit-driven pressures, any
OL,12,Ffinancial surpluses are reinvested for
OL,13,Fthe benefit of our customers, to
OL,14,Fimprove services, support vulnerable
OL,15,Fhouseholds and address environmental
OL,16,Fchallenges."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@LO]
