OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FReacting to the case, a Welsh Labour
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Welsh Labour will
OL,8,Fcreate a new Welsh water watchdog,
OL,9,Fintroduce a new Clean Water Bill for
OL,10,FWales, and will have a dedicated fund
OL,11,Fto crack down on water pollution."
OL,13,FThe Welsh Conservatives said they
OL,14,Fwould improve bathing water quality
OL,15,Fwith "modern technology".
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/23
