OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FThey added: "The Welsh Conservatives
OL,7,Fwill scrap Natural Resources Wales and
OL,8,Freplace it with an independent, fit-
OL,9,Ffor-purpose regulator to ensure
OL,10,Fenvironmental rules are enforced
OL,11,Fproperly."
OL,13,FDr Ellie Chowns, leader of the
OL,14,FParliamentary Green Party and MP for
OL,15,FNorth Herefordshire, described
OL,16,Fpollution in waterways as "a national
OL,17,Fscandal" and said "much more" needs to
OL,18,Fbe done to tackle the problem -
OL,19,Fincluding taking the water sector into
OL,20,Fpublic ownership.
OL,26,@nD@MOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/23
