PN,46119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FShe added: "It also includes properly
OL,7,Fresourcing the Environment Agency so
OL,8,Fthey have the funding and enforcement
OL,9,Fcapabilities they need, supporting
OL,10,Ffarmers to make the transition to
OL,11,Friver-friendly farming practices, and
OL,12,Fintroducing Water Protection Zones in
OL,13,Fareas like the Wye Catchment where
OL,14,Faction is most urgently needed to
OL,15,Fbring our waterways back to health."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/23
