OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru said it is "committed" to
OL,7,Freducing pollution in our waterways. A
OL,8,Fspokesperson for the party said:
OL,9,F"We'll set new and enforceable targets
OL,10,Fto reduce pollution in our rivers and
OL,11,Fseas, based on the 'polluter pays'
OL,12,Fprinciple and prosecuting serious and
OL,13,Fserial offenders as necessary.
OL,15,F"We'll also better support farmers to
OL,16,Fadopt new technologies and practices
OL,17,Fto reduce agricultural water pollution
OL,18,Fby implementing a new science-led,
OL,19,Foutcomes based approach - moving
OL,20,Fbeyond the outdated 'farming by
OL,21,Fcalendar'."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/23
