OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FReform said if elected in May, it
OL,7,Fwould create a Welsh Rivers Act "to
OL,8,Faddress sewage discharge
OL,9,Faccountability, reward measurable
OL,10,Fwater quality improvements and we
OL,11,Fsupport a catchment-based targeted
OL,12,Fsystem of nutrient management, instead
OL,13,Fof the failed blanket NVZ that
OL,14,Funfairly punishes farmers".
OL,16,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrat Leader Jane
OL,17,FDodds said her party is the only one
OL,18,F"consistently championing action on
OL,19,Fwater pollution".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G21/23
