OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777299067
OL,3,CHigh Court hears river pollution case
OL,4,Cin landmark legal action
OL,6,FShe said: "We believe the sewage
OL,7,Fscandal must be brought to an end by
OL,8,Fbanning raw sewage discharges into our
OL,9,Fwaterways, stopping unjustified
OL,10,Fbonuses for water company bosses until
OL,11,Fleaks and dumping are eliminated, and
OL,12,Freplacing Ofwat with a tough new Welsh
OL,13,Fregulator with real enforcement powers.
OL,15,F"Natural Resources Wales must be
OL,16,Fproperly funded and equipped so it can
OL,17,Fmonitor and tackle pollution
OL,18,Feffectively. Quite simply, our rivers
OL,19,Flike the Wye deserve urgent action and
OL,20,Flong-term protection for future
OL,21,Fgenerations."
